      "content": "hey, im studying for my con law exam. i'm trying to understand the debate around the recent 2nd amendment rulings. some people say the court is just following the original intent of the founders, but others say they're basically just making up new laws via judicial activism. how would a legal scholar describe the tension between these two approaches?",
